4845S.06P KRISTINA MARTIN, Secretary
AN ACT
To repeal sections 324.001, 324.028, 324.400, 324.402, 324.403, 324.406, 324.409, 324.412,
324.415, 324.418, 324.421, 324.424, 324.427, 324.430, 324.433, 324.436, 324.439,
327.011, 327.031, 327.041, 327.081, 327.381, 327.411, 327.442, 327.451, 537.033,
and 621.045, RSMo, and to enact in lieu thereof twenty-two new sections relating to
interior designers, with penalty provisions and an effective date for certain sections.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Missouri, as follows:
1 Section A. Sections 324.001, 324.028, 324.400, 324.402,
2 324.403, 324.406, 324.409, 324.412, 324.415, 324.418, 324.421,
3 324.424, 324.427, 324.430, 324.433, 324.436, 324.439, 327.011,
4 327.031, 327.041, 327.081, 327.381, 327.411, 327.442, 327.451,
5 537.033, and 621.045, RSMo, are repealed and twenty-two new
6 sections enacted in lieu thereof, to be known as sections
7 324.001, 324.028, 327.011, 327.031, 327.041, 327.081, 327.381,
8 327.411, 327.442, 327.451, 327.700, 327.705, 327.710, 327.720,
9 327.725, 327.730, 327.735, 327.740, 327.745, 327.750, 537.033,
10 and 621.045, to read as follows:
1 324.001. 1. For the purposes of this section, the
2 following terms mean:
3 (1) "Department", the department of commerce and
4 insurance;
